---
title: Burger-Style Beef Bowl with Salad & Sour Cream Pre-Prepped | Three Steps | Ready in 15
description: With pre-chopped, pre-marinated ingredients, our new Fresh & Fast recipes are on the table in just 15 minutes. Perfect for busy weeknights - and busy people.
This week, tuck into your favourite burger flavours with All-American beef and salad on fluffy rice, all topped off with tangy burger sauce and tasty Cheddar cheese.

*Heads-up - you'll need a microwave for this recipe.*
